<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<!--
  This is a sample RimTalk dialogue definition for the Superb Recruitment mod.
  Place this in your RimTalk\Dialogues folder if you have RimTalk installed.
  
  If RimTalk is not installed, the mod will use the simple dialogue window instead.
-->
<Defs>
  
  <RimTalk.DialogueDef>
    <defName>SuperbRecruitment_PersuadeVisitor</defName>
    <label>Persuade Visitor</label>
    <description>A conversation to persuade a visitor to join your colony.</description>
    
    <!-- Starting node -->
    <startNode>greeting</startNode>
    
    <nodes>
      <!-- Greeting Node -->
      <li>
        <id>greeting</id>
        <text>Hello there! Mind if we chat for a bit?</text>
        <responses>
          <li>
            <text>Sure, I have some time.</text>
            <nextNode>topic_choice</nextNode>
          </li>
          <li>
            <text>I suppose so...</text>
            <nextNode>topic_choice</nextNode>
            <effectOnPersuasion>-0.02</effectOnPersuasion>
          </li>
        </responses>
      </li>
      
      <!-- Topic Choice -->
      <li>
        <id>topic_choice</id>
        <text>What would you like to talk about?</text>
        <responses>
          <li>
            <text>Tell me about your colony.</text>
            <nextNode>colony_talk</nextNode>
          </li>
          <li>
            <text>What do you think of this place?</text>
            <nextNode>opinion_talk</nextNode>
          </li>
          <li>
            <text>Ever thought about settling down?</text>
            <nextNode>settlement_talk</nextNode>
          </li>
          <li>
            <text>Actually, never mind.</text>
            <nextNode>end_neutral</nextNode>
          </li>
        </responses>
      </li>
      
      <!-- Colony Talk -->
      <li>
        <id>colony_talk</id>
        <text>We're a tight-knit group working together to build something special. It's not always easy, but it's rewarding.</text>
        <responses>
          <li>
            <text>Sounds interesting. What makes it special?</text>
            <nextNode>colony_special</nextNode>
            <effectOnPersuasion>0.05</effectOnPersuasion>
          </li>
          <li>
            <text>I see. That's... nice.</text>
            <nextNode>topic_choice</nextNode>
            <effectOnPersuasion>0.02</effectOnPersuasion>
          </li>
        </responses>
      </li>
      
      <!-- Colony Special -->
      <li>
        <id>colony_special</id>
        <text>Everyone here has a role, a purpose. We look out for each other. It's more than just survival - it's about building a future.</text>
        <responses>
          <li>
            <text>That does sound appealing...</text>
            <nextNode>recruitment_hint</nextNode>
            <effectOnPersuasion>0.08</effectOnPersuasion>
          </li>
          <li>
            <text>I have my own path.</text>
            <nextNode>end_neutral</nextNode>
            <effectOnPersuasion>-0.03</effectOnPersuasion>
          </li>
        </responses>
      </li>
      
      <!-- Opinion Talk -->
      <li>
        <id>opinion_talk</id>
        <text>It's quite impressive what you've built here. I've seen a lot of settlements, but this one has... character.</text>
        <responses>
          <li>
            <text>We'd love to have someone with your experience.</text>
            <nextNode>recruitment_direct</nextNode>
            <effectOnPersuasion>0.06</effectOnPersuasion>
          </li>
          <li>
            <text>Thanks! We work hard on it.</text>
            <nextNode>topic_choice</nextNode>
            <effectOnPersuasion>0.03</effectOnPersuasion>
          </li>
        </responses>
      </li>
      
      <!-- Settlement Talk -->
      <li>
        <id>settlement_talk</id>
        <text>Sometimes... The wandering life gets tiring. Having a place to call home would be nice.</text>
        <responses>
          <li>
            <text>This could be that home. We'd welcome you.</text>
            <nextNode>recruitment_direct</nextNode>
            <effectOnPersuasion>0.10</effectOnPersuasion>
          </li>
          <li>
            <text>I understand that feeling.</text>
            <nextNode>topic_choice</nextNode>
            <effectOnPersuasion>0.04</effectOnPersuasion>
          </li>
        </responses>
      </li>
      
      <!-- Recruitment Hint -->
      <li>
        <id>recruitment_hint</id>
        <text>You know... we're always looking for good people. Have you ever considered joining a colony?</text>
        <responses>
          <li>
            <text>I... I might consider it.</text>
            <nextNode>end_positive</nextNode>
            <effectOnPersuasion>0.12</effectOnPersuasion>
          </li>
          <li>
            <text>I don't think so. Not my style.</text>
            <nextNode>end_negative</nextNode>
            <effectOnPersuasion>-0.05</effectOnPersuasion>
          </li>
        </responses>
      </li>
      
      <!-- Recruitment Direct -->
      <li>
        <id>recruitment_direct</id>
        <text>That's... actually really kind of you to say. Let me think about it.</text>
        <responses>
          <li>
            <text>Take all the time you need.</text>
            <nextNode>end_positive</nextNode>
            <effectOnPersuasion>0.10</effectOnPersuasion>
          </li>
        </responses>
      </li>
      
      <!-- End Nodes -->
      <li>
        <id>end_positive</id>
        <text>Thanks for the chat. I appreciate it.</text>
        <isEndNode>true</isEndNode>
      </li>
      
      <li>
        <id>end_neutral</id>
        <text>Well, I should get going. Take care.</text>
        <isEndNode>true</isEndNode>
      </li>
      
      <li>
        <id>end_negative</id>
        <text>I think we're done here.</text>
        <isEndNode>true</isEndNode>
      </li>
      
    </nodes>
  </RimTalk.DialogueDef>
  
</Defs>
